com.versant.common.dataservice
Interface VDSIClassListener

All Superinterfaces:
java.util.EventListener
public interface VDSIClassListener
extends java.util.EventListener

The interface for listeners who are interested in events raised by a VDSClass such as an object creation and deletion.

See Also:
